flowchart TD
    X[Input activations x fp16]
    W["Base weights stored in NF4 (4-bit)<br/>FROZEN throughout training"]
    DQ["Dequantize to fp16<br/>(forward pass only)"]
    A["LoRA A (rank r, fp16)<br/>trainable"]
    B["LoRA B (rank r, fp16)<br/>trainable"]
    Plus(("+"))
    Y[Output fp16]
    Grad["Gradients flow ONLY through<br/>LoRA A and B.<br/>Base NF4 weights never updated."]
    Mem["Memory for DistilBERT-base:<br/>Full fine-tune ~268 MB<br/>QLoRA ~22 MB"]

    X --> DQ
    W --> DQ --> Plus
    X --> A --> B --> Plus
    Plus --> Y
    B -.-> Grad
    W --- Mem
